00:06:03.980 --> 00:06:06.080 align:middle line:90%
Inhale left.

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:07.370 align:middle line:90%
Five counts each.

00:06:07.370 --> 00:06:32.360 align:middle line:90%


00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:33.450 align:middle line:90%
That should be one round.

00:06:33.450 --> 00:06:36.070 align:middle line:84%
One round is completing both
sides beginning and ending

00:06:36.070 --> 00:06:36.870 align:middle line:90%
