00:06:36.870 --> 00:06:37.670 align:middle line:90%
Round two.

00:06:37.670 --> 00:07:07.070 align:middle line:90%


00:07:07.070 --> 00:07:09.495 align:middle line:84%
Should be starting the
third and final round.

00:07:09.495 --> 00:07:38.290 align:middle line:90%


00:07:38.290 --> 00:07:45.300 align:middle line:10%
Exhaling everything out of your
left nostril, keeping your eyes

00:07:45.300 --> 00:07:48.810 align:middle line:10%
closed, slowly lower
the right hand down,

00:07:48.810 --> 00:07:52.820 align:middle line:10%
same index finger and thumb
together, palms facing up.

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:56.530 align:middle line:90%


00:07:56.530 --> 00:07:59.750 align:middle line:84%
And I want you to just come into
total stillness for one minute.

00:07:59.750 --> 00:08:02.860 align:middle line:90%


00:08:02.860 --> 00:08:08.990 align:middle line:10%
And with your
abdomen super soft,

00:08:08.990 --> 00:08:12.290 align:middle line:10%
I want you to just lift
your chest up two degrees,

00:08:12.290 --> 00:08:14.125 align:middle line:10%
so just feeling
the sternum rise.

00:08:14.125 --> 00:08:18.080 align:middle line:90%


00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:21.420 align:middle line:10%
And then now bow your
chin towards your heart

00:08:21.420 --> 00:08:25.100 align:middle line:10%
two degrees so you feel
the back of your neck

00:08:25.100 --> 00:08:26.440 align:middle line:10%
slightly lengthen up.

00:08:26.440 --> 00:08:47.340 align:middle line:90%


00:08:47.340 --> 00:08:49.575 align:middle line:90%
Stillness in the whole body.

00:08:49.575 --> 00:08:52.320 align:middle line:90%


00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:54.570 align:middle line:10%
Slowly slide the
tip of your tongue

00:08:54.570 --> 00:09:00.570 align:middle line:10%
along the roof of your mouth
along the smooth, soft palate

00:09:00.570 --> 00:09:03.990 align:middle line:10%
until you feel the rough edge.

00:09:03.990 --> 00:09:05.910 align:middle line:10%
And when you feel
that rough edge,

00:09:05.910 --> 00:09:09.450 align:middle line:10%
you've gone a
little bit too far.

00:09:09.450 --> 00:09:16.020 align:middle line:10%
Bring it back to just
that final smooth edge,

00:09:16.020 --> 00:09:19.260 align:middle line:10%
very gently pressing there.

00:09:19.260 --> 00:09:21.360 align:middle line:10%
This is known as Kechari Mudra.

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:29.700 align:middle line:90%


00:09:29.700 --> 00:09:37.380 align:middle line:10%
Now breathing in, sense
a column of energy,

00:09:37.380 --> 00:09:41.400 align:middle line:10%
of flow coming in through
the crown of your head

00:09:41.400 --> 00:09:46.740 align:middle line:10%
as you inhale, building
and gathering just

00:09:46.740 --> 00:09:47.910 align:middle line:10%
above the navel center.

00:09:47.910 --> 00:09:50.560 align:middle line:10%


00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:55.070 align:middle line:10%
Visualize this as a
white violet light.

00:09:55.070 --> 00:10:00.360 align:middle line:90%


00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:06.960 align:middle line:84%
And as you exhale, I want you
to visualize a column stream

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:12.060 align:middle line:84%
flow of energy coming up from
the bottom tip of the tailbone

00:10:12.060 --> 00:10:17.520 align:middle line:84%
up to the same space just
above the navel center.

00:10:17.520 --> 00:10:23.370 align:middle line:84%
And visualize it as a
white reddish light.

00:10:23.370 --> 00:10:30.150 align:middle line:84%
The union of red inhaling coming
down to the crown of the head,

00:10:30.150 --> 00:10:36.270 align:middle line:84%
purple violet white light
building and gathering

00:10:36.270 --> 00:10:38.730 align:middle line:84%
as you inhale just
above the navel.

00:10:38.730 --> 00:10:41.890 align:middle line:90%


00:10:41.890 --> 00:10:47.260 align:middle line:84%
Exhale from the tailbone
up, reddish white light up

00:10:47.260 --> 00:10:51.340 align:middle line:84%
from the tail bone
building and gathering just

00:10:51.340 --> 00:10:54.360 align:middle line:90%
above the navel center.

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:58.430 align:middle line:84%
And we'll continue with
this union of breath.

00:10:58.430 --> 00:11:02.810 align:middle line:84%
Inhale and exhale purplish
white light coming

00:11:02.810 --> 00:11:10.800 align:middle line:84%
in through the crown on the
inhale, reddish white light

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:16.140 align:middle line:84%
coming up from the
tailbone on the exhale.

00:11:16.140 --> 00:11:17.740 align:middle line:90%
Continuing on your own.

00:11:17.740 --> 00:12:40.450 align:middle line:90%


00:12:40.450 --> 00:12:48.040 align:middle line:10%
Bowing your chin all the way
down in towards the chest,

00:12:48.040 --> 00:12:50.295 align:middle line:10%
take a slow breath
in through your nose.

00:12:50.295 --> 00:12:53.070 align:middle line:10%


00:12:53.070 --> 00:12:55.360 align:middle line:10%
And like you're fogging
a piece of glass,

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:58.120 align:middle line:10%
exhale softly out the mouth,
bringing your hands together

00:12:58.120 --> 00:13:05.390 align:middle line:10%
at the heart center and
slowly opening your eyes.

00:13:05.390 --> 00:13:27.552 align:middle line:90%